00:51:34.800 --> 00:51:41.719
Menm pi ta, pitit mwen yo ak pitit pitit
mwen yo te ale nan Pierce.

00:51:39.599 --> 00:51:46.279
Donk, vwayaj mwen nan Brookline te kòmanse
an 1993

00:51:43.679 --> 00:51:49.519
le Barbara Shay ki se yon moun etonan te
anboche m

00:51:46.280 --> 00:51:51.440
kòm yon pwofesè tanporè nan Lincoln
School.

00:51:49.519 --> 00:51:54.200
Barbara te enkwayab. Um

00:51:52.719 --> 00:51:58.159
Mwen te ap fè etid pou yon diplòm master
nan tan sa a e um

00:51:56.559 --> 00:52:02.639
premye ane mwen te nan ansyen Lincoln
School. Epi kounye a mwen tounen nan

00:52:00.360 --> 00:52:05.879
plas la kòm yon pwofesè nan Pierce School.

00:52:04.679 --> 00:52:10.320
Um apre sa

00:52:07.960 --> 00:52:14.080
ane pwochèn nou te demenaje nan nouvo
Lincoln School la ki pa t rele

00:52:12.920 --> 00:52:18.239
nouvo Lincoln School. Li te ansyen lekòl
la, nouvo lekòl la. Men um e mwen

00:52:15.920 --> 00:52:22.559
te demenaje avèk yo. Mwen te yon um mwen
te travay nan sant aprantisaj la pandan

00:52:19.800 --> 00:52:26.719
mwen te ap fè diplòm mwen e um ane apre sa
mwen te anboche kòm yon

00:52:24.119 --> 00:52:30.879
pwofesè dezyèm ane nan Pierce School pa
Chris Field ki te tou ansyen

00:52:29.039 --> 00:52:34.800
pwofesè mwen nan twazyèm ane. Donk sa te
yon kalite lòt moman ki

00:52:32.599 --> 00:52:38.639
fè wonn nan tan sa.

00:52:34.800 --> 00:52:41.720
Donk pandan 31 dènye ane sa yo mwen te

00:52:38.639 --> 00:52:45.480
gen sipò nan men ak kounye a mwen jwenn
pou sipòte kèk nan pi bèl edikatè yo nan

00:52:44.039 --> 00:52:49.559
monde. Lè mwen te kòmanse nan Pierce mwen
te travay

00:52:47.360 --> 00:52:51.720
kote kolèg ki te zanmi mwen

00:52:49.559 --> 00:52:54.639
pwofesè lè mwen te ale la.

00:52:51.719 --> 00:52:57.759
Yo tout te gen yon gwo enpak sou

00:52:54.639 --> 00:53:00.159
mwen menm ak pwofesè ke mwen ye jodi a.

00:52:57.760 --> 00:53:03.040
Marie Lavelle ki mwen manke anpil

00:53:00.159 --> 00:53:05.440
chak jou se te manman travay mwen. Li te
pran m

00:53:03.039 --> 00:53:09.079
sou zèl li depi premye jou a e kounye a
kòm yon moun ki te nan Pierce

00:53:07.360 --> 00:53:14.279
pou yon bon tan mwen reyalman eseye imite
gid li,

00:53:12.039 --> 00:53:17.199
pasyans li ak lanmou li pou tout

00:53:14.280 --> 00:53:19.040
pwofesè ak timoun yo.

00:53:17.199 --> 00:53:23.360
Pierce se plis pase yon travay pou mwen.
Se kominote mwen. Kote ki kenbe

00:53:21.320 --> 00:53:27.840
souvenirs timoun mwen ak kote pitit mwen
yo te reyisi.

00:53:25.800 --> 00:53:32.600
Ane sa a mwen gen yon timoun nan klas
dezyèm ane mwen ki manman li te nan premye

00:53:30.719 --> 00:53:35.759
klas mwen, mwen regrèt, ki tant li te nan
premye

00:53:32.599 --> 00:53:39.559
klas mwen nan Pierce ak ki manman li

00:53:35.760 --> 00:53:42.920
te nan klas ak pitit gason mwen e tou yon

00:53:39.559 --> 00:53:46.119
Suzanne tou. Um

00:53:42.920 --> 00:53:48.920
Um se yon pwofesè, yon manman, yon

00:53:46.119 --> 00:53:52.840
alumni, ak yon rezidan nan Brookline
reyèlman reyalize sa nan

00:53:51.440 --> 00:53:58.240
li te oblije jere anpil responsabilite
pandan ane yo. Sepandan, mwen pa

00:53:55.480 --> 00:54:00.960
ta chanje anyen, e mwen renmen chak minit
nan

00:53:58.239 --> 00:54:04.079
li. Mwen renmen mache desann nan lari a ak

00:54:00.960 --> 00:54:06.360
jwenn anbrase nan men timoun ki gen 30 ani
ak

00:54:04.079 --> 00:54:11.039
timoun ki gen sèt. Mwen renmen wè yon
ofisye polis Brookline

00:54:09.320 --> 00:54:14.360
epi apre sa reyalize ke ofisye polis sa a

00:54:11.039 --> 00:54:17.440
te nan klas dezyèm ane mwen an.

00:54:14.360 --> 00:54:19.440
E mwen toujou renmen yo kòm yon pati
esansyèl

00:54:17.440 --> 00:54:22.400
nan lekòl la mwen te antre kòm yon

00:54:19.440 --> 00:54:25.000
etidyan premye ane plizyè, plizyè ane de
sa.

00:54:22.400 --> 00:54:28.119
Mwen vle felisite tout moun ki fè li
pandan

00:54:25.000 --> 00:54:30.079
30 oswa 31 ane sa yo.

00:54:28.119 --> 00:54:34.440
Pa chak jou fasil, espesyalman nan tan sa
a nan ane a. Nou tout yon ti jan

00:54:31.760 --> 00:54:38.559
ap fè efò pou rive nan fini an, men pou sa
yo ki te la

00:54:36.280 --> 00:54:41.080
otankou tout moun, nou konnen ki sa ki yon

00:54:38.559 --> 00:54:43.552
kominote espesyal Brookline ye. Se konsa,

00:54:41.079 --> 00:54:45.572
mèsi anpil paske nou tout avèk nou.

00:54:43.552 --> 00:54:45.572
[applause]

00:54:49.440 --> 00:54:53.280
Mèsi, Susan. Stephanie Poon.

00:54:54.032 --> 00:54:56.052
[applause]

00:55:02.000 --> 00:55:07.400
Mèsi anpil poutèt evènman sa a ki vrèman

00:55:04.280 --> 00:55:09.200
bèl. Sa se yon plezi pou koute

00:55:07.400 --> 00:55:13.439
tout moun. Se konsa, mwen te panse a de
bagay

00:55:11.559 --> 00:55:16.960
uh ki ap mennen mwen pou jodi a. Ki sa ki
kenbe mwen vivan pandan 30 ane? Paske sa se yon

00:55:15.639 --> 00:55:21.400
long tan. E ki sa mwen remake uh sou sa

00:55:18.840 --> 00:55:23.200
ki chanje ak sa ki rete menm depi mwen

00:55:21.400 --> 00:55:26.440
te kòmanse nan BHS nan '90s yo.

00:55:27.039 --> 00:55:29.960
Men sa mwen jwenn.

00:55:28.800 --> 00:55:33.920
Bagay ki fè travay sa a posib e menm, mwen
ta ka di,

00:55:31.559 --> 00:55:36.799
de fwa kontan se moun mwen

00:55:33.920 --> 00:55:39.720
antoure pa um um BHS. Sa yo se elèv mwen
yo

00:55:36.800 --> 00:55:42.959
an premye, um ki, byenke yo ta ka poze
mwen yon kesyon

00:55:41.039 --> 00:55:45.880
sou yon bagay mwen jis

00:55:42.960 --> 00:55:48.840
di, yo se vrèman rezon ki fè mwen
kontinye.

00:55:45.880 --> 00:55:51.559
Yo san fen kirye, mwen fè anpil
fristrasyon,

00:55:48.840 --> 00:55:54.840
siyèl, entelijan, travay di, e yo toujou
fè mwen panse sou kijan mwen ka

00:55:53.320 --> 00:55:58.840
fè travay mwen pi byen. Sa a se tan ane a
kote mwen vrèman

00:55:56.480 --> 00:56:02.600
pran tan pou reflechi sou ki jan ane
pwochèn, mwen pral vrèman jwenn yon fason

00:56:00.559 --> 00:56:06.599
pou fè travay sa a e rezoud tout pwoblèm
edikasyon yo.

00:56:05.159 --> 00:56:09.480
Lòt moun ki bò kote mwen nan Brookline
High ki fè sa a posib se

00:56:07.880 --> 00:56:12.760
kòlèg mwen yo. Mwen renmen yo.

00:56:10.800 --> 00:56:17.000
Si mwen pa t gen moun ki entelijan,
reflechi, ak swaf pou ede bò kote mwen,

00:56:14.440 --> 00:56:20.119
mwen ta fòse e mwen ta kite. Lòt bagay ki
ka fè sa a

00:56:18.440 --> 00:56:25.119
toute 30-an sa a posib se tout bagay mwen
te kapab fè.

00:56:23.000 --> 00:56:28.519
Mwen te mentò nouvo pwofesè nan Brookline
pandan plizyè ane atravè

00:56:26.599 --> 00:56:33.159
pwogram Teachers Mentoring Teachers. Lè
yon gwoup kòlèg ki gen eksperyans mwen

00:56:30.519 --> 00:56:37.119
te gen menm konvèsasyon an pou 15èm fwa
sou kijan istwa nèvyèm ane a te disfonksyonèl,

00:56:35.239 --> 00:56:41.880
ak kijan nou te pa satisfè ak tras sosyal
ki te mennen nan 70% elèv nou yo ki pran onè,

00:56:39.639 --> 00:56:46.280
nou, ansanm ak Biwo Enseignement ak
Aprantisaj, Sipèintandan an, ak

00:56:44.840 --> 00:56:50.440
Komite Lekòl la (School Committee), te
kreye WISP. Lè yon lòt gwoup kòlèg

00:56:48.519 --> 00:56:53.639
created WISP. When a different group of
colleagues

00:56:51.840 --> 00:56:57.400
te plenyen sou senioritis ki afekte elèv
ki nan dezyèm semès la,

00:56:55.880 --> 00:57:01.320
ak fason yo sèl enterè nan edikasyon sa a
te sanble se te nòt yo olye de aprantisaj yo,

00:56:59.079 --> 00:57:05.400
nou te kreye yon klas senior eksperimantal
ki rele EPIC. Bay pwofesè opòtinite

00:57:03.840 --> 00:57:09.920
pou sèvi ak gwo eksperyans ak fòmasyon nou
yo pou envante

00:57:07.519 --> 00:57:12.679
nouvo bagay ak rezoud pwoblèm se sa ki fè
nou santi nou byen.

00:57:09.920 --> 00:57:16.319
Mwen te sipòte tou paske mwen te ka gade
pwòp pitit mwen yo pase nan

00:57:14.880 --> 00:57:20.120
lekòl Brookline, e pa gen anyen ki ka pi
byennere pase wè pitit ou ap ranmase

00:57:17.920 --> 00:57:24.359
bénéfice efò kòlèg ou yo, santi lanmou ak
swen

00:57:22.920 --> 00:57:28.120
ki tonbe sou yo, ak konnen ou pa janm ka
remèt sa, sèlman

00:57:26.719 --> 00:57:32.359
avanse. Pwogram frè materyèl la ki te
pèmèt

00:57:30.559 --> 00:57:35.680
mwen ak mari mwen voye pitit nou yo,

00:57:33.840 --> 00:57:38.720
yon nan yo se la dèyè sa a,

00:57:35.679 --> 00:57:40.919
atravè PSB te ban mwen yon sans pi fon nan
angajman pou plas sa a. Kòm mari mwen

00:57:38.719 --> 00:57:44.639
Brian Lee Brian te di dènyèman, sa te
literalman vle di ke mwen te gen po nan

00:57:42.960 --> 00:57:47.199
jwèt la. Eske mwen vle fè lekòl mwen pi
bon ke li ka ye, pou mwen angaje tèt mwen

00:57:46.079 --> 00:57:52.199
pou elèv mwen yo menm jan kòlèg mwen yo te
angaje pou de pitit mwen yo?

00:57:50.440 --> 00:57:56.039
Ou parye sa. Donk, dezyèm bagay mwen te

00:57:53.760 --> 00:57:59.360
ap panse sou se sa ki chanje ak sa ki rete
menm jan an.

00:57:57.159 --> 00:58:03.160
Epi reyèlman de premye pwen yo soti pi
bonè sou elèv yo ak kòlèg yo,

00:58:01.760 --> 00:58:08.280
sa yo pa chanje. Mwen vle di, yo
literalman chanje. Yo se

00:58:06.559 --> 00:58:12.560
moun diferan. Um, pou pi fò pati, uh, men
lespri a, enèji a,

00:58:09.559 --> 00:58:16.400
enspirasyon an, ak plezi a, sa a se
sanble.

00:58:14.159 --> 00:58:19.880
Anpil bagay chanje, ladan l.

00:58:17.599 --> 00:58:21.759
Lè mwen te kòmanse, mwen te gen binders ki
te chaje ak plan leson,

00:58:19.880 --> 00:58:26.640
e mwen te ekri sou yon tablo kriz.

00:58:26.800 --> 00:58:29.720
Mwen te pase yon gwo kantite tan jis

00:58:28.159 --> 00:58:34.719
ap eseye aprann tout bagay mwen bezwen

00:58:29.719 --> 00:58:37.359
pou anseye, jwe ak anseye.

00:58:34.719 --> 00:58:40.319
Elèv yo te tèt yo,

00:58:37.360 --> 00:58:42.400
men yo te mwens enkyete.

00:58:40.320 --> 00:58:45.960
Li te sanble ke pwofesè yo te jeneralman
plis respekte.

00:58:46.679 --> 00:58:53.039
Bagay yo ki soutni mwen yo pa konplike
oswa ezoterik.

00:58:50.800 --> 00:58:55.400
Se bagay sa yo ki soutni nou tout.

00:58:53.039 --> 00:58:57.920
Travay ki gen sans ak bon moun,

00:58:55.400 --> 00:59:01.720
nouvo defi ki enteresan,

00:58:57.920 --> 00:59:05.720
plezi, ri, ak pafwa jwa,

00:59:01.719 --> 00:59:08.230
ak vakans ete. [applaudisman]

00:59:11.079 --> 00:59:15.440
Mèsi, Steph. Kounye a, èske sa a se Malia
oswa Malia?

00:59:14.960 --> 00:59:21.329
Malia. Malia Scott. Mèsi.

00:59:19.309 --> 00:59:21.329
[applaudisman]

00:59:28.079 --> 00:59:33.400
Donk, um nan dènye rankont espesyal pou
matematik nou an,

00:59:31.159 --> 00:59:35.759
nou pase tan

00:59:33.400 --> 00:59:38.960
tradui karyè nou nan Brookline

00:59:35.760 --> 00:59:40.920
nan ane, jou, èdtan, ak minit,

00:59:38.960 --> 00:59:44.480
paske se egzakteman sa nou fè pou plezi
nan depatman matematik lan.

00:59:43.320 --> 00:59:46.960
Donk,

00:59:44.480 --> 00:59:50.800
tanpri pase m' sa.

00:59:46.960 --> 00:59:52.800
Donk, 32 ane de sa, lè mwen te kòmanse
pwogram

00:59:50.800 --> 00:59:57.360
mastè mwen an ak staj tout ane nan Lincoln
School,

00:59:55.400 --> 01:00:01.880
mwen pa t menm konnen ki sa pwogram frè
materyèl la ye, ni ki jan li ta ka gen yon gwo

01:00:00.199 --> 01:00:05.800
efè sou lavi fanmi mwen.

01:00:03.199 --> 01:00:10.160
Yon semèn ak yon demi de sa, mwen leve sou
sèn nan e mwen te gradye ti pitit mwen an

01:00:08.079 --> 01:00:14.440
nan Brookline High. Mwen santi yon gwo
rekonesans pou

01:00:12.559 --> 01:00:18.159
edukasyon etonan timoun mwen yo te resevwa
isit la nan Brookline.

01:00:15.719 --> 01:00:22.719
Malgre twa timoun mwen yo, youn ladan yo
la,

01:00:19.760 --> 01:00:25.320
um yo se aprenan ki totalman diferan,

01:00:22.719 --> 01:00:27.639
yo tout te fleri, yo te jwenn defi, ak

01:00:25.320 --> 01:00:30.160
yo te beni ak pwofesè ki eksepsyonèl ki

01:00:27.639 --> 01:00:32.599
te ede yo reyalize potansyèl yo.

01:00:30.159 --> 01:00:35.559
Mwen vrèman rekonesan ke pwogram frè
materyèl la

01:00:32.599 --> 01:00:38.000
te fè tout sa posib,

01:00:35.559 --> 01:00:41.719
paske li pa sèlman te sipòte fanmi mwen,
men li te pèmèt mwen devwe lavi pwofesyonèl mwen

01:00:39.760 --> 01:00:46.679
pou kominote Brookline.

01:00:44.159 --> 01:00:50.119
5,856 jou lekòl de sa,

01:00:48.360 --> 01:00:55.159
mwen pa t janm ka imajine mwen ta sèvi
pifò nan karyè pwofesyonèl mwen kòm

01:00:52.400 --> 01:00:58.639
yon espesyalis matematik, donk liv ak
lekti te toujou pasyon mwen depi mwen te ti.

01:00:57.119 --> 01:01:02.400
Sepandan, pandan premye tan mwen nan

01:01:00.719 --> 01:01:07.639
Brookline, mwen te gen privilèj pou
kolabore ak moun ki gen konpetans ak talan konsa.

01:01:04.760 --> 01:01:10.640
edikatè matematik tankou Rose
Christiansen,

01:01:07.639 --> 01:01:12.759
Nancy Buel, ak Hillary Pastor.

01:01:10.639 --> 01:01:16.760
Yo ede m re-nan fòme idantite mwen kòm yon
matematisyen e yo enspire m pou

01:01:15.360 --> 01:01:20.640
pran avantaj sou devlopman pwofesyonèl pou
kontinyèlman rafine pwòp

01:01:19.280 --> 01:01:25.719
ansèyman mwen. Pi enpòtan an, yo revele
veritab

01:01:22.920 --> 01:01:28.519
lè kontan pou anseye matematik e

01:01:25.719 --> 01:01:32.559
yo enstile nan mwen kwayans ke chak elèv
se yon moun ki kapab aprann matematik.

01:01:31.320 --> 01:01:36.679
Wòl espesyalis matematik mwen toujou

01:01:34.519 --> 01:01:38.920
santralize sou kolaborasyon e mwen

01:01:36.679 --> 01:01:41.759
trè chans pou m travay bò kote

01:01:38.920 --> 01:01:43.880
kolèg ki se aprenan pou tout lavi.

01:01:41.760 --> 01:01:48.160
Yo sipòte, defye, e enspire m pou
kontinyèlman grandi. Se te yon vre

01:01:46.239 --> 01:01:51.399
privilej pou kolabore ak edikatè briyan
konsa ak pou travay avèk

01:01:49.760 --> 01:01:55.960
yo pou jwenn fason kreyatif pou bay
matematik lavi.

01:01:53.599 --> 01:01:59.480
Yo pouse m pou eseye bagay difisil ak pou
depase limit mwen e mwen fyète

01:01:57.880 --> 01:02:04.679
anpil sou tout sa nou reyalize ansanm
pandan ane yo.

01:02:02.360 --> 01:02:09.159
38,064 èdtan lekòl pase, mwen pa t ankò

01:02:06.920 --> 01:02:13.359
rekonèt enpak yon lidè lekòl vizyonè ki
sipòte.

01:02:11.440 --> 01:02:16.360
Jodi a, mwen sensèman rekonesan pou

01:02:13.360 --> 01:02:19.240
mwen te travay anba direktè eksepsyonèl
tankou

01:02:16.360 --> 01:02:22.719
Barbara Shay, Andrew Bott, ak kounye a
Brian Dinitzio.

01:02:20.760 --> 01:02:26.279
Yo te montre gwo lafwa nan mwen e atravè
sipò inisyativ matematik mwen nan

01:02:24.639 --> 01:02:31.440
Lincoln, yo te ban mwen konfians, espas,
ak tan pou vrèman

01:02:29.159 --> 01:02:33.639
inovatif, pou eseye nouvo bagay, ak pou

01:02:31.440 --> 01:02:38.079
grandi kòm edikatè matematik.

01:02:33.639 --> 01:02:38.079
E finalman, 2,283,840

01:02:39.480 --> 01:02:45.079
minit lekòl pase, mwen pa t ka imajine

01:02:43.079 --> 01:02:48.960
ke veritab kontan mwen te santi lè mwen te
kòmanse travay ak elèv yo

01:02:47.239 --> 01:02:52.599
ta toujou nan kè pratik mwen

01:02:48.960 --> 01:02:55.119
jodi a. Mwen renmen se yon pwofesè.

01:02:52.599 --> 01:02:59.480
Mwen fleri nan demantib zouti mwen pa bon
an matematik e mwen jwenn reyèl

01:02:58.079 --> 01:03:04.480
satisfaksyon nan konnen chak elèv se yon
moun ak pwòp fòs inik ak

01:03:01.599 --> 01:03:07.480
defi. Nan edikasyon, pa janm gen

01:03:04.480 --> 01:03:11.039
yon apwòch ki fè tout moun. Pou satisfè
bezwen elèv ki pi ranfòse yo,

01:03:09.000 --> 01:03:16.000
mwen dwe kontinyèlman grandi, reflechi, ak
aprann.

01:03:13.440 --> 01:03:19.480
Mwen viv pou moman aha sa yo ki batay

01:03:16.000 --> 01:03:21.360
lè yon konsèp konplèks finalman klike

01:03:19.480 --> 01:03:23.519
ak eklatman konfyans la lè

01:03:21.360 --> 01:03:26.599
elèv yo kòmanse rekonèt tèt yo

01:03:23.519 --> 01:03:29.320
kòm rezolvatè pwoblèm ki kapab.

01:03:26.599 --> 01:03:32.920
Kijan mwen chans pou m toujou ap anseye
nan Brookline 137

01:03:33.280 --> 01:03:39.349
30,400

01:03:35.559 --> 01:03:41.369
segond apre sa. Mèsi.

01:03:39.349 --> 01:03:41.369
[aplodi]

01:03:46.159 --> 01:03:51.480
Mèsi, Malia. Um, mwen vle raple moun ki
toujou kanpe ke gen

01:03:49.639 --> 01:03:56.240
twa chèz isit la, anpil chèz la sou bò
gòch mwen. Donk,

01:03:54.360 --> 01:03:57.039
pouki ou pa detann ou? Chita, tanpri.

01:03:56.239 --> 01:04:02.273
N ap la pou yon ti tan anko.

01:03:58.519 --> 01:04:04.293
Dako, pwochen moun, Yasmin Shariff.

01:04:02.273 --> 01:04:04.293
[aplodi]

01:04:07.280 --> 01:04:09.760
